          <div class="media-block__carousel--6-up">      <script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"http://schema.org","@type":"NewsArticle","mainEntityOfPage":{"@type":"WebPage","@id":"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/news/athlete-feature-nic-bean"},"headline":"Factory Racing Athlete Feature: Nic Bean","datePublished":"2018-Oct-Mon","publisher":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Santa Cruz Bicycles","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/sites/all/themes/scb2017/assets/img/ref.svg#santa-cruz-logo"}},"description":"If you\u2019ve stopped by the Santa Cruz showroom sometime in the last couple of years, there\u2019s a chance you\u2019ve talked to Nic Bean or he\u2019s set up your demo bike. He's a quiet, hard-working local who\u2019s built like Richie Rude, but with better hair, a part-time Santa Cruz employee and full-time bike racer.After tackling the regional California Enduro Series races and successfully chasing the U21 National Enduro Series Champ title in 2017, Nic made the decision to step up to the big leagues and race internationally for 2018 - a season that sent the 19 year old across the pond for the first time to race a total of five EWS races starting in Montagnes du Caroux, France and wrapping up recently in Finale Ligure, Italy.[[{\"fid\":\"9942\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"5\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"5\"}}]]Puzzling a customer's Tallboy demo. [[{\"fid\":\"9912\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"1\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"1\"}}]]Nic charging in Whistler for Round 6 of the EWS. Listen to what he had to say about his race below.[[{\"fid\":\"9919\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"4\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"4\"}}]]The stoke is high for the young gun as he wraps up his first EWS season healthy and hungry for more in 2019.Nic\u2019s main goal for the season was to gain as much experience as possible racing at the international level without setting any unreal expectations on himself. This is key to a young rider\u2019s development since racing is taxing as it is without the added pressure of setting the bar too high early in your career.[[{\"fid\":\"9913\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"2\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"2\"}}]]Foot-out-flat-out in Ainsa.After wrapping up in Finale a couple weeks back, he\u2019s back to the drawing board and resting up a bit before he starts training harder than ever for the 2019 season, which will be his last year in the EWS U21 category. Nic\u2019s goals for next season are to continue to progress as a bike racer and all around rider while ideally finishing in the Top 10 overall.[[{\"fid\":\"9914\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"3\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"3\"}}]]Follow Nic\u2019s progress and adventures on instagram.","articleBody":"<p>If you\u2019ve stopped by the Santa Cruz showroom sometime in the last couple of years, there\u2019s a chance you\u2019ve talked to <a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/rider/nic-bean\">Nic&nbsp;Bean</a> or he\u2019s set up your demo bike. He's a quiet, hard-working local&nbsp;who\u2019s built like Richie Rude, but with better hair, a part-time Santa Cruz employee and full-time bike racer.</p><p>After tackling the regional California Enduro Series races and successfully chasing the U21 National Enduro Series Champ title in 2017, Nic made the decision to step up to the big leagues and race internationally for 2018 - a season that sent the 19 year old across the pond for the first time to race a total of five EWS races starting in Montagnes du Caroux, France and wrapping up recently in Finale Ligure, Italy.</p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9942\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"5\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Santa Cruz Factory Demo - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean setting up a customer's demo Tallboy 3. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"5\"}}]]<em><strong>Puzzling a customer's <a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/tallboy\">Tallboy</a>&nbsp;demo.</strong></em>&nbsp;</p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9912\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"1\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles -  EWS Whistler - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Whistler\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"1\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>Nic charging in Whistler for Round 6 of the EWS. Listen to what he had to say about his race below.</strong></em></p><p><em><strong><iframe allow=\"autoplay\" frameborder=\"no\" height=\"20\" scrolling=\"no\" src=\"https://w.soundcloud.com/player/?url=https%3A//api.soundcloud.com/tracks/516263523&amp;color=%23ff5500&amp;inverse=false&amp;auto_play=false&amp;show_user=true\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9919\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"4\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"4\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>The stoke is high for the young gun as he wraps up his first EWS season healthy and hungry for more in&nbsp;2019.</strong></em></p><p>Nic\u2019s main goal for the season was to gain as much experience as possible racing at the international level without setting any unreal expectations on himself. This is key to a young rider\u2019s development since racing is taxing as it is without the added pressure of setting the bar too high early in your career.</p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9913\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"2\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Ainsa - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Ainsa\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"2\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>Foot-out-flat-out in Ainsa.</strong></em></p><p>After wrapping up in Finale a couple weeks back, he\u2019s back to the drawing board and resting up a bit before he starts training harder than ever for the 2019 season, which will be his last year in the EWS U21 category. Nic\u2019s goals for next season are to continue to progress as a bike racer and all around rider while&nbsp;ideally finishing in the Top 10 overall.</p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9914\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"3\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Sven Martin\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - EWS Finale Ligure - 2018\",\"title\":\"Nic Bean in Finale\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"3\"}}]]<em><strong>Follow Nic\u2019s progress and adventures on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nicbean_/\">instagram</a>.</strong></em></p>","image":["https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/files/ewsfinale18_an3x4796_0.jpg"]}</script>  
