tributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"title\":\"Dougie Fresh\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"14\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>Dougie Fresh was on hand keeping the Syndicate rolling as usual and also had the chance to sample&nbsp;all the fresh tracks.</strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9828\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":false,\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"6\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":false,\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"6\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>No chamois allowed!</strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9829\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia  - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Ratboy at Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"7\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia  - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Ratboy at Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia  - 2018\",\"title\":\"Ratboy at Trans-Cascadia\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"7\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>The Rat, ripping.</strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9830\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Greg Minnaar at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"8\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Greg Minnaar at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"title\":\"Greg Minnaar at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"8\"}}]]</p><div><em><strong>How now brown pow? Corners like this were the hard-earned outcome of <a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/news/2018-trans-cascadia-trail-work\" target=\"_blank\">dig parties that the Trans-Cascadia crew</a> held throughout the summer.</strong></em></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>===== IMAGE GRID 2 goes here =====<br>[[{\"fid\":\"9832\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"The masterminds behind Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"10\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"The masterminds behind Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"title\":\"The masterminds behind Trans-Cascadia. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"10\"}}]]</div><p><em><strong>The masterminds behind Trans-Cascadia since day one - Alex, Nick, and Tommy. Without their hard work and devotion to good trails&nbsp;this beautiful event wouldn't exist.&nbsp;</strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9833\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz podium sweep at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"11\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz podium sweep at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"title\":\"Santa Cruz podium sweep at Trans-Cascadia. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"11\"}}]]</p><p><em><strong>Santa Cruz with the podium sweep&nbsp;at Trans-Cascadia. Loris 1st, Francois 2nd, and Luca 3rd. We'll take it!</strong></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9853\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Juliana Bicycles Podium at 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Juliana Bicycles Podium at the 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"19\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Juliana Bicycles Podium at 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"Juliana Bicycles Podium at the 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Juliana Bicycles Podium at 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"title\":\"Juliana Bicycles Podium at the 2018 Trans-Cascadia\",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"19\"}}]]</p><p><em><b>Juliana takes one and two. Emily Slaco 1st and Kim Hardin 2nd.</b></em></p><p>[[{\"fid\":\"9834\",\"view_mode\":\"default\",\"fields\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"But you'll drink the drink. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"},\"link_text\":null,\"type\":\"media\",\"field_deltas\":{\"12\":{\"format\":\"default\",\"field_file_image_alt_text[en][0][value]\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"field_file_image_title_text[en][0][value]\":\"But you'll drink the drink. \",\"field_img_caption[und][0][value]\":\"Mike Thomas\"}},\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"Santa Cruz Bicycles - Trans-Cascadia - 2018\",\"title\":\"But you'll drink the drink. \",\"class\":\"media-element file-default\",\"data-delta\":\"12\"}}]]</p><p><b><i>That's a wrap. Catch a recap of the daily video drops over <a href=\"https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/en-US/news/2018-trans-cascadia-video-recap\">here</a>. See you next year!&nbsp;</i></b></p>","image":["https://www.santacruzbicycles.com/files/mthomasphoto_tc_day4_039_0.jpg"]}</script>  
